longBusinessSummary: Helo Corp., a technology company, provides wearable devices for use in the quantified-self wellness market. The company's wearable devices and related applications offer its end-users with health-related knowledge acquired through self-tracking. Its products include Helo LX that gathers the wearer's bio-parameter data; Helo LX+, which offer continuous monitoring of bio-parameters; and HELO Extense, a peripheral device that pairs with smartphone and tracks sugar trends. The company was formerly known as World Technology Corp. and changed its name to Helo Corp. in October 2018. Helo Corp. is based in Miami, Florida.
